Users in the system should be able to:
-Sign up / create user.
-Use the sign up details to obtain a valid JWT token to be used for other requests.
-User management - Update user details{password only}

-User should be able to post a blog.
-User should be able to update a blog post. If its owned by user.
-User should be able to delete a blog post. If its owned by user.
-User should be able to view all blog posts.
-User should be able to view a blog post by its id.
-View all blogs for a certain user.

-User should be able to comment on a blog.
-User should be able to see a blog and its comments.
-User should be able to update a comment.
-User should be able to delete a comment.
